| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-0137 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5fc80f37-8d7c-5be7-a9f1-9303567c672a"
